{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"language","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"language","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The language code (e.g., “en”, “de”, “fr”, “es”) or nil to reset to device language"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Override the device language for Pushwoosh to enable:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sending notifications in a specific language"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Language-based segmentation"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Supporting in-app language switching"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Must be a lowercase two-letter code according to ISO-639-1 standard."}]},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Support in-app language selection:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class LanguageManager {","","    static let shared = LanguageManager()","","    var currentLanguage: String {","        didSet {","            applyLanguageChange()","        }","    }","","    func applyLanguageChange() {","        \/\/ Update Pushwoosh language for targeted notifications","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","","        \/\/ Update user tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"language\": currentLanguage,","            \"language_changed_date\": Date()","        ])","","        \/\/ Update app UI","        Bundle.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","        NotificationCenter.default.post(name: .languageDidChange, object: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"App language changed to: \\(currentLanguage)\")","    }","","    func resetToDeviceLanguage() {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(nil)","        currentLanguage = Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\"","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“zh” (Chinese), “ja” (Japanese), “ko” (Korean), “ru” (Russian)"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","title":"setLanguage:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setLanguage:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setLanguage:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setLanguage:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Sets custom application language for localized notifications.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setlanguage:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","title":"PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshC